#: includes/class-frontend-controller.php:351
msgid "The comment was updated."
msgstr "댓글을 수정했습니다."

#: includes/class-frontend-controller.php:347
msgid "The comment was permanently deleted."
msgstr "댓글을 영구 삭제했습니다."

#: includes/class-updater.php:303
msgid "Comment Management is missing its Composer dependencies. Install a release package or run composer install."
msgstr "Comment Management의 Composer 의존성이 없습니다. 릴리스 패키지를 설치하거나 composer install을 실행하세요."

